---
// ABOUTME: Roadmap section showing planned features for keytun.
// ABOUTME: Displays upcoming features as cards with keycap icons and status badges.
---

<section class="section section-dark" id="roadmap">
	<div class="container">
		<h2>Roadmap</h2>
		<p class="section-sub">What's coming next.</p>
		<div class="roadmap-grid">
			<div class="roadmap-card">
				<div class="keycap-small roadmap-icon">🔐</div>
				<h3>Password-protected sessions</h3>
				<p>Host sets a password when starting a session. Clients must enter it before keystrokes flow.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="roadmap-card">
				<div class="keycap-small roadmap-icon">👁</div>
				<h3>Read-only mode</h3>
				<p>Join as a viewer — see the terminal output without being able to type. Great for demos and teaching.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="roadmap-card">
				<div class="keycap-small roadmap-icon">🐧</div>
				<h3>Linux system mode</h3>
				<p>OS-level keystroke injection on Linux via xdotool/ydotool, matching the existing macOS system mode.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="roadmap-card">
				<div class="keycap-small roadmap-icon">🔔</div>
				<h3>Connection notifications</h3>
				<p>Audible and visual notifications when a client joins or leaves your session.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="roadmap-card">
				<div class="keycap-small roadmap-icon">📡</div>
				<h3>Latency indicator</h3>
				<p>Round-trip time in the client status bar so you know whether lag is keytun or your connection.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="roadmap-card">
				<div class="keycap-small roadmap-icon">✋</div>
				<h3>Connection approval</h3>
				<p>Host approves each client before keystrokes start flowing. Full control over who gets access.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.roadmap-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(300px, 100%), 1fr));
		gap: 20px;
		margin-top: 48px;
	}

	.roadmap-card {
		background: var(--bg-card);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		padding: 28px 24px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		transition: border-color 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s, transform 0.25s;
	}

	.roadmap-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--border-accent);
		box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 79, 56, 0.08), 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3), 0 0 28px rgba(255, 79, 56, 0.07);
		transform: translateY(-3px);
	}

	.roadmap-icon {
		margin-bottom: 16px;
	}

	.roadmap-badge {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 6px;
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.06em;
		padding: 3px 10px;
		border-radius: 50px;
		width: fit-content;
		margin-bottom: 12px;
	}

	.roadmap-badge.planned {
		color: var(--accent-amber);
		background: rgba(232, 168, 48, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(232, 168, 48, 0.2);
	}

	[data-theme="dark"] .roadmap-badge.planned {
		background: rgba(255, 217, 61, 0.1);
		border-color: rgba(255, 217, 61, 0.2);
	}

	.roadmap-badge.in-progress {
		color: var(--accent-mint);
		background: rgba(61, 168, 84, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(61, 168, 84, 0.2);
	}

	[data-theme="dark"] .roadmap-badge.in-progress {
		background: rgba(107, 203, 119, 0.1);
		border-color: rgba(107, 203, 119, 0.2);
	}

	.roadmap-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}

	.roadmap-card p {
		color: var(--text-dim);
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.roadmap-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
